Find country, state/province, subnational2, IBA, or BCR codes

Source: R/codes.R
region_search.Rd

Search for the correct codes to identify countries, states/provinces, subnational2 areas, Important Bird Areas (IBA), or Bird Conservation Regions (BCR). These are then used in the nc_data_dl() and nc_count() functions.

region_search(name = NULL, type = "country")

Arguments

name

Character. The location name to search for
type

Character. One of "country", "statprov", "subnational2", "iba", or "bcr". The type of information to return.

Value

A data frame with the relevant codes and other information

Examples


region_search("Mexico", type = "country")   # MX
#>   country_code country_name country_name_fr
#> 1           MX       Mexico         Mexique

region_search("Yucatan", type = "statprov") # Yucatán
#>   country_code statprov_code statprov_name_es statprov_name statprov_name_fr
#> 1           MX            YP          Yucatán       Yucatán          Yucatán
region_search("Alberta", type = "statprov") # AB
#>   country_code statprov_code statprov_name_es statprov_name statprov_name_fr
#> 1           CA            AB          Alberta       Alberta          Alberta

region_search("Edmonton", type = "subnational2") # CA.AB.11
#>   country_code statprov_code subnational2_code          subnational2_name
#> 1           CA            AB          CA.AB.11 Division No. 11 - Edmonton
#>   ebird_code
#> 1   CA-AB-EL
region_search("Brandon", type = "subnational2")  # CA.MB.07
#>   country_code statprov_code subnational2_code             subnational2_name
#> 1           CA            MB          CA.MB.07 Division No. 7 - Brandon Area
#>   ebird_code
#> 1   CA-MB-SE

region_search("hays reservoir", type = "iba") # AB075
#>   iba_site    iba_name_fr latitude statprov area_ha alt_min       iba_name
#> 1    AB075 Hays Reservoir 50.06152       AB    8.99     785 Hays Reservoir
#>   nearest_town bcr ncc_region alt_max longitude status
#> 1         Hays  11         26      NA  -111.832      G
region_search("rainforest", type = "bcr")     # 5
#>   bcr                    bcr_name                        bcr_name_es
#> 1   5 Northern Pacific Rainforest Bosque Lluvioso del Pacífico Norte
#>                                        bcr_name_fr
#> 1 Forêts pluviales du nord de la côte du Pacifique
